data.description: Lovely 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom ranch home in 55+ Carillon Lakes community! Primary bedroom has a wonderfully large en suite with double sinks and a separate bathtub and shower. The property boasts hardwood laminate flooring recently done in the last 5 years, which allows for easy movement throughout the home. Additional improvements include- freshly painted (October 2023), new furnace and a/c units (2021), a new water heater (2023), and washer and dryer (appx 5 yrs ago). Enjoy a sense of peace and privacy, as this home is tucked away in a wonderful spot with your back door facing nothing but an open field.  The beautiful gated community also includes a clubhouse, indoor and outdoor swimming pools, golf course, tennis courts, and even a playground for young visitors! This home has been loved by the original owner for 18 years, and is awaiting its new owner! Welcome home!
